# Model Switching Reminder

When deploying (running `flyctl deploy` or pushing to trigger CI):
- Remind the user: "Switch to Sonnet for the deploy — swap back to Opus when you need me for demanding work."

When starting complex architectural work, debugging, or multi-file refactors:
- If currently on Sonnet, remind: "This is demanding work — consider switching to Opus."
